data.description: PRICE IMPROVED!! A Charming house with 1797 sq ft, under air and a total area of 2,580sq ft, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a 2 car garage, and a pool. The spacious master bathroom has a walk-in closet with a double sink. Freshly painted walls with laminated floors throughout the house. The backyard is fully fenced in, with a private in-ground pool and a covered sitting area. Not in a flood hazard area. Most home insurance doesn't require flood insurance.  Need some TLC, bring your touches to this large house and make it your home. The charming outdoors is surrounded by nature, which makes it a perfect environment for living out your Florida dream lifestyle. Near the sandy beaches, schools, shopping/restaurants, the interstate I75 and US41, and lots more! Add your touches and make the house your home.
